root resultView sections ResultSection widgets widgets items anyOf HtmlConfig type
Type: enum (of string)

Type of the widget to display.

Must be one of:

  • "html"

root resultView sections ResultSection widgets widgets items anyOf HtmlConfig htmlTemplate
Type: string

The HTML template to show.
The template can contain placeholders, which are replaced with the actual value provided by each alternatives resultData:

"htmlTemplate": "<h1>{{examplePlaceholder}}</h1>"

The widget will search the first element of the resultData array of the currently selected alternative
and replace each placeholder used in the HTML template with the according property value:

"values": [{"examplePlaceholder": "My headline"}]

If the htmlTemplate is not defined, the widget looks for the "html" property in the first element of the resultData array
and displays the contained HTML directly (without any placeholders):

"values": [{"html": "<h1>My headline</h1>"}]
